data.description: Introducing the Perfect Haven in Woodruff, South Carolina! Nestled on a serene cul-de-sac lot at 120 W Longfield Ln, this stunning property offers the ideal blend of comfort and style. Boasting 5 bedrooms, 4 bathrooms, and a generous 3,500 square feet, this home provides ample space for everyone. As you approach, you'll be captivated by the charming pond behind the home, creating a picturesque backdrop for your daily retreat. The custom shed with electricity adds a touch of practicality, perfect for a workshop or extra storage. Inside you will discover the seamless integration of modern design and functionality. The new carpet upstairs adds a fresh touch, complementing the open concept layout that enhances the spacious feel of the home. The large kitchen is a culinary enthusiast's dream, featuring stainless steel appliances, granite countertops, and an abundance of cabinet space. The main floor hosts a bedroom and a full bath, offering convenience and flexibility for guests or a home office. The attached two-car garage ensures hassle-free parking and easy access to your abode. Natural light floods the interiors through numerous windows, creating a warm and inviting atmosphere throughout. Upstairs, a versatile loft space awaits, providing additional room for relaxation or entertainment. The remaining 4 bedrooms include an oversized primary suite, complete with a luxurious tub, shower, and a walk-in closet. Location is key, and this property doesn't disappoint. Conveniently situated near 101, I-85, BMW, and Michelin, commuting is a breeze. Enjoy an easy trip to downtown Spartanburg, downtown Greenville, and even Charlotte, North Carolina. Don't miss the opportunity to make this Woodruff gem your home. Schedule a viewing today and experience the epitome of modern living in the heart of South Carolina!
